    "further suggested that LLMs could achieve higher patient satisfaction by offering timely and accurate services 25.",
    "However, the present study demonstrated greater satisfaction using LLMs combined with RAG than using LLMs alone.",
    "Accurate question answering is crucial in the medical field.",
    "For example, patients with breast cancer require precise and timely information to achieve effective recovery.",
    "The present study demonstrated that the integration of RAG technology using a local knowledge base significantly improved the accuracy of the GPT responses."
